        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1947-04-24T20:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1947-04-24T20:00:00-05:00" n="813" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d813">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">740.00119 Control (Korea)/4–1047: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Ambassador in China</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Stuart</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1947-04-24T20:00:00-05:00">April 24, 1947—8 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>480. Following tel received from Tokyo. Dept suggests that in your discretion you
                    approach Chinese Govt as indicated in final paragraph.</p>
                <p>[Here follows text of telegram No. 78, April 10, printed <hi rend="italic">supra</hi>.]</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Acheson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
